'''胡克反应'''（Hooker reaction，1936）指某些[[萘醌|萘醌]]衍生物（如[[黄钟花醌|黄钟花醌]]）用[[碱性|碱性]][[高锰酸钾|高锰酸钾]]发生[[降解|降解]]，以[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]的形式失去一个[[亚甲基|亚甲基]]单位，生成烃基链缩短的产物。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=On the Oxidation of 2-Hydroxy-1,4-naphthoquinone Derivatives with Alkaline Potassium Permanganate|author=Samuel C. Hooker|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1936|volume=58|issue=7|pages=1174–1179|doi=10.1021/ja01298a030}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=On the Oxidation of 2-Hydroxy-1,4-naphthoquinone Derivatives with Alkaline Potassium Permanganate. Part II. Compounds with Unsaturated Side Chains|author=Samuel C. Hooker and Al Steyermark|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1936|volume=58|issue=7|pages=1179–1181|doi=10.1021/ja01298a031}}</ref>

